{"tid":1836150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】封城前武漢人大逃亡　自私女當旅行發住燒去主題公園","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:12:08.000Z","uid":216745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f2b838c851cb6422adf62aec6ec574975ac950","tid":1836150,"uid":216745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎確診個案爆發更擴至多國，內地人人自危，今日（23日）上午10時起武漢更被當局勒令封城，官方要求市民無特殊原因不要離開武漢。惟急於求生的居民懶理，獲知消息反而紛紛秘密「逃離武漢」，大批逃出者微博分享逃離過程，就算已現發燒、頭痛及咳嗽等疑似「中招」病徵的人，毫無公德照樣逃出，更稱靠食藥紓緩病情後當去旅遊，轉赴上海迪士尼或西安鼓樓等熱門旅遊點遊玩，遭網民怒斥缺德。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/425502/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%89%8D%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%83%E4%BA%A1-%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%95%B6%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%8F%E7%87%92%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F425502%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2580%2583%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BD%258F%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=16ab1957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/425502/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%89%8D%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%83%E4%BA%A1-%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%95%B6%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%8F%E7%87%92%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92</a><br />\n<br />\n多L謝無名女仕去海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so